  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served between 7am and 10am. Help yourself to a selection of cold meats, cheeses, bread, cereals, yoghurt, boiled eggs and fresh coffee.  </p>
<p>In the evenings enjoy three courses of traditional Italian cuisine in the hotel restaurant. They specialise in <span>local dishes. </span>If you're travelling with children, the hotel can offer early meals for them at 6.30pm. </p>
<p>Christmas and New Years gala meal included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
