  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Serenella is a small hotel in a great spot in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a> where you can expect traditional Italian hospitality.</p>
<h2>Location</h2>
<p>You will be based close to the slopes with the Cretaz chairlift and the ski school meeting point less than 100 metres away.</p>
<p>It's a couple of minutes walk there, but on your return you can ski back 50 metres or so from the boot room.</p>
<p>You'll also find Cervinia's restaurants, shops, pubs and clubs right your doorstep. </p>
<h2>Traditional Italian Style</h2>
<p>The hotel lounge bar is decorated with wooden paneling in a typical alpine style. It's a nice place to relax on the comfy sofas and enjoy a tipple after a day on the mountain.</p>
<p>On sunny days we love sitting out on the sun loungers on the small terrace. The rooms are decorated in the same alpine style, but have a fresh, modern feel. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Serenella the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
